{"tid":277852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作4年月入1.1萬　大學生：養唔到家","createTime":"2017-06-10T03:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T07:34:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ec7d977079c281e360f230ed4a30d7d0bdb5d1","tid":277852,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170610/s00006/98188235eee8b3f5bd61e7baa31a37c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170610%2Fs00006%2F98188235eee8b3f5bd61e7baa31a37c3.jpg&h=826cef0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】本港貧富懸殊惡化，高學歷收入未必高，有90後大學畢業生工作逾4年，至今每月收入僅約1.1萬元，即與初中學歷人士的月入中位數看齊；為省開支，她要節衣縮食外，假日也多選免費的行山或行商場等消遣，其「低消費活動」在朋友圈中更一呼百應，因許多朋友都有大學資格，有工作能力，「但份工養不到家」。<br />\n<br />\n上班帶飯 放假圖書館涼冷氣<br />\n<br />\n一家五口居於沙田公屋的27歲阿迪（化名），大學主修環境科學，2012年畢業時，感覺興趣不在本科，沒從事工程或環境監察工作，改到律師樓任文職，起薪每月9000元，後來轉至政府任合約員工，每月有1.1萬元，合約完結額外獲10%約滿酬金。2014年時，她裸辭赴澳洲參加工作假期。<br />\n<br />\n2015年回港後，她按興趣投身社福界，在社區中心任助理項目幹事。因無相關經驗及學歷，起薪點僅1萬多元，較同級低，今年加薪至1.1萬元。扣除家用、交通及電話費等，每月約有6000元零用，但本港物價高企，「出次街，食餐飯便沒了百幾元」。為省開支，她上班帶飯，盡量行路，減少乘車，2015年後沒去過旅行，盡量到深水埗購物；放假多行山或逛商場，近日天氣熱便到圖書館，笑言「慳埋冷氣費」。<br />\n<br />\n她欲報讀課程考獲相關資格，有助升職，唯課程費用昂貴又欠資助，短時間無法完成。阿迪直言政府扶貧措施欠長遠，資源分配不均，本港在職貧窮人數亦上升，令其「低消費活動」總是一呼百應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030853727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030853727&d=K4QdYdPxXcZORePJNRKbpDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6faae761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030853727&h=0c3f633d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030853727</a>"},{"pid":"974022892e1068bc5126ad5a1d4c31e84e0f553a","tid":277852,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"讀垃圾料 當然搵唔到錢啦"},{"pid":"104abb7c9381ca2f21efbadcccbeb9fa478d827b","tid":277852,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307a066bc607b84f2e5170a744a04f7fcdf07217","tid":277852,"uid":3002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"大佬你自己一出黎係要做文員仔，再wh 返黎轉行由低做起，怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條路自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8595cfa20bfde504d9e4415ddcf844061ccea944","tid":277852,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aae5f0a1581237ce24dfa6415aa53cfdaf5f651e","tid":277852,"uid":516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"呢D case根本係自己唔度好條career path"},{"pid":"d4a7676835da9b7151c947ac985be54c5599a823","tid":277852,"uid":20302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"讀完個大學 on99 做份濕尻文職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ce90f8020464ab332f91c9c9de109d22e01d5f","tid":277852,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"自己問題大d"},{"pid":"763f82a000c7876fc0072e554fffa5644f63f1dc","tid":277852,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"香港地學人講興趣<br />\n等乞食喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f88fb0759a774df78ede668a9f809160ffd29a1","tid":277852,"uid":34910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀環境科學等乞食</blockquote><br />\n關咩事 佢都無諗過自己想做乜<br />\n讀完環境去律師樓做 做一排又去wh返嚟做社福界 係咁轉行由低做起人工點會高"},{"pid":"72ffa249bf6d6b88aedfb59448f84cc3134fac57","tid":277852,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re